Marketplace. The interface is colorful, has more flair, and some cool 
features like ‚ÄòMixview‚Äô that let you quickly see related albums, songs, 
or other users related to what you‚Äôre listening to. Clicking on one of 
those will center on that item, and another set of ‚Äúneighbors‚Äù will come
 into view, allowing you to navigate around exploring by similar 
artists, songs, or users. Speaking of users, the Zune ‚ÄúSocial‚Äù is also 
great fun, letting you find others with shared tastes and becoming 
friends with them. You then can listen to a playlist created based on an
